### User Report APIs

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create a new report (User)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "This is a test report about a bug I found in the system.",
  "type": "Bug"
}

### 2. Get all my reports (User)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/my-reports
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get a specific report by ID (User)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Delete a report (User)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reports/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
